methods.compactDuplicates:
Remove all adjacent values from chunkToCompact, except the last value in any adjacent run. The keyIndices are
 parallel to the chunkToCompact; and when a value is removed from chunkToCompact it is also removed from
 keyIndices

 Additionally, verify that the elements are properly ordered; returning the first position of an out of order
 element.

:param chunkToCompact: (io.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.WritableChunk<? extendsio.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.Attributes.Any>) - the values to remove duplicates from
:param keyIndices: (io.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.WritableLongChunk<io.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.Attributes.KeyIndices>) - the key indices parallel to chunkToCompact
:return: (int) the first position of an out-of-order element, or -1 if all elements are in order
